					<msContents class="lccn.loc.gov/sh85013597" rend="visible">
						<summary>The commentary of Japheth ben Ali ha-Levi on the book of Proverbs.</summary>
						<textLang mainLang="he" otherLangs="jrb">Hebrew, Judeo-Arabic</textLang>
						<msItem n="0" rend="visible" class="lccn.loc.gov/sh85013597">
							<locus from="1r" to="129r"/>
							<title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Perush Mishle</title>
							<title xml:lang="he">פרוש משלי</title>
							<author key="http://viaf.org/viaf/54984961">
								<persName key="http://viaf.org/viaf/54984961" xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Japheth ben Ali, ha-Levi,‏ active 10th century </persName>
								<persName key="http://viaf.org/viaf/54984961" xml:lang="he">יפת בן עלי, הלוי</persName>
							</author>
							<note>
								<p>The pointed Hebrew text, accompanied by an Arabic translation, is embodied.</p>
								<p>Contains: 4:24-6:1, 6:6-9, 6:12-21, 6:23-35, 8:6-36, 9:7-10:10, 10:12-12:24, 13:8-14:11, 14:30-18:1, 18:19-19:9.</p>
								<p>Of the Hebrew text the following parts are preserved: 5:1-6:5, 6:17-35, 8:19-29, 8:32-9:3, 9:10-10:10, 10:13-12:24, 13:9-14:11, 14:31-18:1, 18:20-19:9.</p>
								<p>Has a scribal subscription at the end.</p>
								<p>Masoretic division into section and קרי are marked in the margins.</p>
							</note>
							<listBibl>
